name: Lisa Ann
description:
Talent agent, podcast host, director and actress Lisa Ann, most famous for her accurate portrayal of the very first woman to become governor of Alaska chasing her political ambition for Vice Presidency in the historical drama "Who's nailin' Paylin?"

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Some style embeds or model triggerwords heavily direct the way faces are drawn. Inpainting circumvents this pretty well.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
